    "visualHierarchy": "Visual hierarchy is established through vertical stacking of components, with the most prominent element (primary login button) strategically placed below input fields. Social login buttons are presented with a horizontal arrangement below the primary button, distinguishing them from the primary login action. Font sizes and styling will further enhance the visual hierarchy.",
